{"word":"G2885 - κοσμέω - kosméō - kos-meh'-o - Adorn","slug":"G2885","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">κοσμέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>kosméō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>kos-meh'-o"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Adorn"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03BA;&#x03BF;&#x03C3;&#x03BC;&#x03B5;&#x0301;&#x03C9; - kosmeo&#x0304;</b> - <i>kos-meh'-o</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/G2889\">G2889</a>; to <i>put in</i> proper <i>order</i>, that is, <i>decorate</i> (literally or figuratively); specifically to <i>snuff</i> (a wick): - adorn, garnish, trim."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G2886\">G2886</a>, <a href=\"#/G2887\">G2887</a>, <a href=\"#/G2889\">G2889</a>"}]}